July 28 2005 Sheldon Lee-Wen
	Add a CONTROLLER directive to the media-detect.conf file to allow
	the plugin to execute a different command to control the program.
	This is needed for some programs where the binary, and the program
	that controls are different.
July 26 2005 Sheldon Lee-Wen
	Adding beep-media-player to the media-detect.conf file.
	Changed the JUK entry in the media-detect.conf file to use the JUK
	plugin instead of dcop.
